root: ^Hi there Hanae. I see you're ready to leave our little Lily Town huh?
^It's a little sad, but I do have to get back to the Capital to report my work.
^I'm so glad this village was my first village as my role a Royal Flower Picker.
^Maybe the Goddess Flora is really looking out for her people.
^Well, I wouldn't sell yourself short little one. Your efforts are the reason our village is starting to blossom again. I'm sure all the other Royal Flower Pickers would be proud of ya.
^The people here will always be grateful for all your hard work. And I'm sure future villages you'll help would also really appreciate it.
^When you put it like that, I guess I'll have to continue giving it my all.
^I will truly miss this Lily Town, but as long as everyone is happy here because of the flowers I picked, then there's nothing more fulfilling than that.
^Well said Hanae. Now I don't want to keep you waiting on trip. Be safe out there, and thank you for all you've done.
